      <title>捷普在調查中讓執行長威爾森帶薪休假</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/jabil-places-ceo-wilson-paid-leave-amid-investigation-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[電子元件製造商捷普週四表示，自 4 月 15 日起，該公司已安排執行長肯尼斯威爾森 (Kenneth Wilson) 帶薪休假，等待完成與公司政策相關的調查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/jabil-places-ceo-wilson-paid-leave-amid-investigation-2024-04-18/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 22:57:06 GMT</pubDate>
