      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bentley-systems-explores-options-amid-takeover-interest-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，市值近 160 億美元的工程軟體公司 Bentley Systems 正在探索包括在吸引收購興趣後出售的選項。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bentley-systems-explores-options-amid-takeover-interest-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid>
